summary: I WAS DRIVING NORTH ON  HWY 86 FROM THE CITY OF IMPERIAL CA. WHEN I SET MY CRUISE CONTROL AT 65 MPH SUDDENLY START GOING UP AND DOWN WITH THE SPEED ( GOING UP TO 67 AND DOWN TO 64) WITH NO VEHICLES IN FRONT OF ME. I ARRIVE TO MY HOUSE AND AFTER HEARING PROBLEMS WITH THE STALLING  ON THE CR-V MODELS , MY HUSBAND CHECK THE OIL AND IT SMELL A LOT TO  GASOLINE.
